      "span_text": "Those in the P125109 lineage contained φSE10, φSE12, φSE12A and φSE14 and φSE20, while those in the LK5 lineage lacked φSE20 but contained the RE-2010 sequence described by Zheng et al., located in the same region as in LK5"
